[27/09/2018 21:07:55] <font color="#00ff00">se ignoran mutuamente</font>
[27/09/2018 21:07:55] <font color="#00ff00">y son incapaces de entenderse.</font>
[27/09/2018 21:08:00] <font color="#00ff00">El chico extranjero,</font>
